    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers generally to the beginning of the Baroque style and period, particularly the Italian Baroque from about 1585 to 1625.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
